descript.abstract: The boundaries of the Voting Precincts for Pasco County have been delineated in this layer based on information provided by the Pasco County Supervisor of Elections Office.
descript.purpose: The Voting Precinct boundaries have been used to determine the boundaries of the Congressional Districts, Senate Districts, the House Districts, Commissioner Boundaries and Municipalities.

procstep.procdesc: The original dataset was acquired by Pasco County GIS from the Pasco County Supervisor of Elections Office. The attribute table was modified to include the precincts for the Congressional, Senate, House, Board of Commissioners and School Board Districts and the Municipalities.
